{"id": "art-136", "label": "Art. 136", "title": "Art. 136", "slug": "art-136", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 136 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1858136881\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2263\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1858136881\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span> reprezentând, individual sau împreun&#259;,\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 10% din capitalul social vor putea\ncere <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> s&#259; desemneze unul sau mai <span\nclass=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;i</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>îns&#259;rcina&#355;i</span> s&#259; analizeze anumite <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iuni</span> din gestiunea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; întocmeasc&#259; un raport, care\ns&#259; le fie înmânat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, totodat&#259;, predat\noficial consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv\ndirectoratului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> consiliului de supraveghere,\nprecum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cenzorilor sau auditorilor interni ai <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, dup&#259; caz, spre a fi analizat <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a se propune m&#259;suri corespunz&#259;toare.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1828573276\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2262\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1828573276\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, va include raportul întocmit în conformitate cu alin.\n(1) pe ordinea de zi a urm&#259;toarei adun&#259;ri generale a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Onorariile <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;ilor</span>\nvor fi suportate de societate, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span>\ncazurilor în care sesizarea a fost f&#259;cut&#259; cu rea-<span class=SpellE>credin&#355;&#259;</span>.</span></p>"}